# CODEOWNERS
#
# Requests review from the owners of matching files when a PR touches them.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners
#
# Rules:
#   - .gitignore-style patterns map paths to owners.
#   - The LAST matching rule wins, so keep broad defaults first and specific
#     paths later.
#   - Owners need write access. Prefer teams (@org/team) over individuals so any
#     member can unblock a PR.
#
# The repo is solo today, so @aswini-kumar-11 owns everything. Replace it with
# a real GitHub account or team as the org grows.

